-- Madoff Trustee to Seek Approval for Payout to Customers
-- B y   L i n d a   S a n d l e r
-- 2012-06-25T14:35:35Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-25/madoff-trustee-to-seek-approval-for-payout-to-customers.html
The liquidator of  Bernard Madoff ’s
firm will ask a judge to approve a second payment to the con
man’s investors after the U.S. Supreme Court declined to
hear an appeal over the payment formula, according to a
statement today by the Madoff trustee.  To contact the reporter on this story:
